### Welcome.

I try to write something to enjoy github:

### Sqlite Viewer
Just a simple sqlite database viewer.I need not to find browser plugin or full functional tool for only view a sqlite db.
It also support db encrypted by sqlcipher.
[Sqlite Viewer](https://github.com/isee15/Sqlite-Viewer)
